You set me up!
So you could take the money!

736
01:02:34,125 --> 01:02:36,377
You talked Ju-yeong into this!

737
01:02:36,461 --> 01:02:38,671
You did that to steal all of my money!

738
01:02:38,755 --> 01:02:40,506
How could you do this to me?

739
