How could you?

740
01:03:36,813 --> 01:03:39,857
I didn't expect to see you here.
I'm glad you are here.

741
01:03:40,358 --> 01:03:41,818
How dare you show up here?

742
01:03:43,402 --> 01:03:45,279
I was curious about his recovery.

743
01:03:46,030 --> 01:03:47,907
I want him to gain consciousness

744
01:03:49,033 --> 01:03:50,243
more than anyone.

745
01:03:51,494 --> 01:03:53,579
And I have the right to be here

746
01:03:53,663 --> 01:03:56,833
