Come back to me with Ho-su.

770
01:05:16,913 --> 01:05:18,497
The three of us can start over.

771
01:05:19,665 --> 01:05:21,626
Bring Li-sa too if you want.

772
01:05:21,709 --> 01:05:23,044
I'm different now.

773
01:05:23,544 --> 01:05:24,712
I'll support you.

774
01:05:26,005 --> 01:05:27,298
I'll be successful.

775
01:05:28,549 --> 01:05:30,426
More successful than your husband.

776
01:05:39,352 --> 01:05:40,978
Where's Mr. Lee's cell phone?

777
01:05:42,563 --> 01:05:46,067
I know you took it.
There's something in it, isn't there?

778
01:05:46,984 --> 01:05:49,570
That's why you remembered
to take it even when he…

779
01:05:53,658 --> 01:05:55,785
HYEON-SEONG

780
01:05:59,956 --> 01:06:01,999
Get out. Let's talk outside.

781
01:06:02,083 --> 01:06:03,918
Let's talk outside. Please?

782
01:06:09,507 --> 01:06:11,884
I'm on my way up.
Are you still in the room?

783
01:06:15,012 --> 01:06:16,472
Please.

784
01:06:22,979 --> 01:06:25,231
Why are you out here?
Why didn't you go in?

785
01:06:25,314 --> 01:06:27,441
I didn't want to go in by myself.

786
01:06:29,986 --> 01:06:31,570
It's bad. He's still unconscious.

787
01:06:32,154 --> 01:06:33,531
Is Li-sa's therapy over?

788
01:06:33,614 --> 01:06:37,076
Oh, my. She should be done soon.
I'll go check on her.

789
01:06:37,159 --> 01:06:40,037
I'll go too.
We should work on this together.

790
01:06:40,538 --> 01:06:41,414
She's our daughter.

791
01:06:55,261 --> 01:06:58,639
You won't do it without Ms. Jeong?
Come on, don't do this again.

792
01:06:59,223 --> 01:07:00,933
This is an important time for you.

793
01:07:01,017 --> 01:07:03,102
This is a great chance
to fix their prejudice.

794
01:07:03,185 --> 01:07:05,855
Exactly. That's why
I must do it with Ms. Jeong.

795
01:07:06,897 --> 01:07:08,441
This was a joint project.

796
01:07:08,524 --> 01:07:10,943
If she drops out,
what will people say about that?

797
01:07:11,027 --> 01:07:12,820
How many more times must I tell you?

798
01:07:12,903 --> 01:07:16,615
You must distance yourself
from Ms. Jeong to protect yourself.

799
01:07:16,699 --> 01:07:19,368
Exactly. I asked you several times
why that's the case.

800
01:07:30,838 --> 01:07:33,841
You don't love me. Wake up!

801
01:07:33,924 --> 01:07:36,218
If you approach her again,

802
01:07:36,302 --> 01:07:38,220
I won't be able to stop her.

803
01:07:38,304 --> 01:07:41,766
If this video reaches the public,
your career is over before it even starts.

804
01:07:42,433 --> 01:07:43,809
This isn't what it looks like.

805
01:07:43,893 --> 01:07:45,519
Of course you'd say that.

806
01:07:45,603 --> 01:07:46,687
It's not!

807
01:07:46,771 --> 01:07:49,231
Right. I don't know
what happened between you two.

808
01:07:49,315 --> 01:07:52,610
What's important is that people will
only believe what they want to.

809
01:07:52,693 --> 01:07:54,862
And people will believe
Ms. Jeong over you.

810
01:07:55,446 --> 01:07:56,989
This is a lie!

811
01:07:59,784 --> 01:08:02,745
That's not true! It's a lie!

812
01:08:08,292 --> 01:08:09,418
It's not true.

813
01:08:14,507 --> 01:08:15,966
That's a lie.

814
01:08:22,640 --> 01:08:25,643
I lived here only briefly,
but I still have a lot of stuff to pack.

815
01:08:27,686 --> 01:08:30,106
It was so easy to start.

816
01:08:30,189 --> 01:08:31,774
But breaking up is difficult.

817
01:08:34,318 --> 01:08:36,570
Why do we always make the same mistake?

818
01:08:38,864 --> 01:08:40,241
What brings you here anyway?

819
01:08:43,911 --> 01:08:46,956
I know I don't deserve it,
but I'm here to ask you for a favor.

820
01:08:48,707 --> 01:08:49,959
Please stop Woo-jae.

821
01:08:50,751 --> 01:08:52,753
He will listen to you.

822
01:08:54,713 --> 01:08:56,090
Remember what you told me?

823
01:08:57,299 --> 01:08:59,343
That I would destroy myself

824
01:08:59,844 --> 01:09:02,596
because of my victim mentality.

825
01:09:04,431 --> 01:09:06,559
You were right, as you can see.

826
01:09:07,768 --> 01:09:11,730
And I can now understand
that you will not crumble

827
01:09:12,565 --> 01:09:13,899
no matter how hard I try.

828
01:09:15,985 --> 01:09:18,779
It was impossible to achieve something

829
01:09:18,863 --> 01:09:22,408
only out of hatred and resentment.

830
01:09:27,121 --> 01:09:28,539
But Woo-jae isn't like me.

831
01:09:29,039 --> 01:09:32,209
His feelings for you,
whatever they may be…

832
01:09:33,878 --> 01:09:36,088
He firmly believes that it's love.

833
01:09:36,630 --> 01:09:40,301
It's your responsibility
to cut off his obsession with you.

834
01:09:41,093 --> 01:09:42,052
Hae-won.

835
01:09:42,136 --> 01:09:43,679
You said…

836
01:09:44,638 --> 01:09:46,891
you would never break down like me. Right?

837
01:09:49,018 --> 01:09:52,938
I will be watching you to see

838
01:09:53,022 --> 01:09:56,275
if you can do what you so proudly claimed.

839
01:10:35,689 --> 01:10:36,732
Why'd you come?

840
01:10:40,152 --> 01:10:41,862
Ms. Lee called me.

841
01:10:42,738 --> 01:10:44,073
She's worried about you.

842
01:10:46,075 --> 01:10:48,327
She doesn't know that we broke up.

843
01:10:53,999 --> 01:10:57,503
SEO WOO-JAE
GU HAE-WON

844
01:10:58,671 --> 01:10:59,880
DIVORCE AGREEMENT

845
01:10:59,964 --> 01:11:01,382
Should I tell her?

846
01:11:12,017 --> 01:11:13,644
Hui-ju came to me.

847
01:11:16,981 --> 01:11:19,984
A proud woman like her asked me for help.

848
01:11:22,695 --> 01:11:24,238
She asked me to stop you.

849
01:11:26,240 --> 01:11:28,409
That's how disgusted she must be by you.

850
01:11:30,369 --> 01:11:32,037
Do you still not see it?

851
01:11:33,247 --> 01:11:37,501
She abandoned you. Completely.

852
01:11:46,385 --> 01:11:48,220
If things worked out for you two,

853
01:11:50,055 --> 01:11:52,308
I would have only hated you.

854
01:11:56,353 --> 01:11:58,188
But now I pity you.

855
01:12:01,567 --> 01:12:05,404
I don't hate you. I pity you.

856
01:12:09,283 --> 01:12:10,534
Does it hurt?

857
01:12:11,785 --> 01:12:12,786
Is it painful?

858
01:12:15,539 --> 01:12:17,416
Is this what they call karma?

859
01:12:18,584 --> 01:12:20,419
There really must be a God.

860
01:12:21,253 --> 01:12:24,506
Seeing how you get to feel the way I felt

861
01:12:25,591 --> 01:12:28,052
after all of my efforts
to get it through to you.

862
01:12:40,147 --> 01:12:41,440
I'll file the form.

863
01:13:05,589 --> 01:13:06,632
Li-sa.

864
01:13:07,883 --> 01:13:09,343
Let's order food for dinner.

865
01:13:10,052 --> 01:13:11,845
We should do it before Mom gets back.

866
01:13:12,679 --> 01:13:13,806
What should we eat?

867
01:13:14,681 --> 01:13:15,933
When is she coming home?

868
01:13:16,725 --> 01:13:19,103
Well, she should be here pretty soon.

869
01:13:20,062 --> 01:13:21,188
We can order it now.

870
01:13:21,772 --> 01:13:24,066
Chicken. I want fried chicken, Dad.

871
01:13:24,149 --> 01:13:26,443
Make sure to order soda too.

872
01:13:26,527 --> 01:13:28,737
Chicken? Sure.

873
01:13:29,238 --> 01:13:30,739
Is Ho-su really going to England?

874
01:13:33,200 --> 01:13:34,159
Why?

875
01:13:36,495 --> 01:13:38,205
But I don't want to go.

876
01:13:38,789 --> 01:13:39,873
Are you going too?

877
01:13:40,791 --> 01:13:42,000
Dad, you too?

878
01:13:43,585 --> 01:13:45,796
-What about Mom?
-Don't send him abroad.

879
01:13:48,590 --> 01:13:51,176
He's going to school.
You studied there too.

880
01:13:51,260 --> 01:13:52,970
Ho-su doesn't want to go.

881
01:13:53,720 --> 01:13:55,264
Why did you let Grandma decide?

882
01:13:58,350 --> 01:14:01,145
-We can discuss it later.
-Is it because of Mom again?

883
01:14:33,343 --> 01:14:36,305
Woo-jae. Hold on.

884
01:14:41,518 --> 01:14:43,395
Woo-jae, don't do anything rash.

885
01:14:46,982 --> 01:14:47,983
Wait.

886
01:14:51,278 --> 01:14:52,321
Woo-jae!

887
01:15:28,357 --> 01:15:29,775
I can't let you go like this.

888
01:15:43,872 --> 01:15:44,873
Hui-ju…

889
01:15:57,678 --> 01:15:59,096
If I can't have you,

890
01:16:00,389 --> 01:16:01,890
nobody can have you.

891
01:17:23,513 --> 01:17:28,518
Subtitle translation by: Won-hyang Son

